        <p style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);font-size:1rem;max-width:520px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.75;">Four steps from postcode check to doorstep delivery. No subscriptions, no hidden fees.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1.25rem;">

        <div style="background:#F4F8F5;border:1px solid #E2EDE5;border-radius:1.25rem;padding:2rem 1.75rem;transition:all .3s;">
          <div style="font-size:3rem;font-weight:800;color:rgba(10,74,47,.1);line-height:1;margin-bottom:1.25rem;font-family:var(--font-heading);">01</div>
          <div style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-text-primary);margin-bottom:.5rem;">Check your postcode</div>
          <p style="font-size:.875rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);line-height:1.65;margin:0;">We deliver to Melbourne metro suburbs. Enter your postcode to confirm before you shop.</p>
        </div>

