          <p style="font-size:.875rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Top up with bulk produce, pantry staples, or this week's specials.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="background:#F4F8F5;border:1px solid #E2EDE5;border-radius:1.25rem;padding:2rem 1.75rem;transition:all .3s;">
